Name: certbot-dns-constellix
Version: 0.1.2
Summary: Constellix DNS Authenticator plugin for Certbot
Home-page: https://github.com/Constellix/certbot-constellix
Author: Jessica Smith
Author-email: jsmith@constellix.com
